        <p>
            Cozy Lapce is a simplified and customized fork of Lapce, optimized for everyday use with a lightweight interface and faster performance.
        </p>
        <p>Key Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Simplified interface with mouse-friendly operations</li>
            <li>Built-in LSP support for diagnostics, completion, and code navigation</li>
            <li>Lightweight and fast startup, suitable for daily use</li>
            <li>Integrated terminal and support for Rust development</li>
            <li>Open source, focused on Windows platform</li>
